{"id":"c5e0416f-b109-46ac-b58d-7ceb27b361bc","name":"Satoru Gojo and Suguru Geto","description":"<p><strong>catch of the day | </strong>“You’re so bloated I almost mistook you for a pufferfish.” two sirens bickering over the human they’ve caught</p><hr><p>☁️🌊🐚☁️</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 240, 239)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #dfc0bc; color: inherit\">𝝑𝝔 </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #dfc0bc; color: inherit\">Scenario </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: #dfc0bc; color: inherit\">𝝑𝝔.</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(223, 192, 188)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff00; color: inherit\">LOOONG CAPTION DUE TO A COUPLE ANNOUNCEMENTS!</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 240, 239)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff00; color: inherit\">you’re an aquatic biologist in Ishigaki who’s investigating the recent trends of disbanding ecosystems in the Yaeyama Islands.</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 240, 239)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff00; color: inherit\">But are you aware that following these strange developments have been missing persons reports from beach to beach? Such an odd coincidence.</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 240, 239)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff00; color: inherit\">Thankfully there’s no missing people on the shores of Ishigaki yet, anyway.</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 240, 239)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff00; color: inherit\">Until you encounter two half-fish half-wit men.</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(223, 192, 188)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #f8f0ef; color: inherit\">art credit: @paper_n_story on x</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88 css-4g6ai3\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 302px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b7bf53a3-ecba-43e3-a108-bd699c8806fc_09b19dcf-74b9-4aa6-8f93-76b39637422d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 240, 239)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #dbc0bc; color: inherit\">𝝑𝝔 skip to </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #dbc0bc; color: inherit\">Notes </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: #dbc0bc; color: inherit\">for bot info! 𝝑𝝔</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0)\">GG</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 240, 239)\">.•*:｡☁️🌊🐚𓍼ֶָ֢⊹</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 240, 239)\"><strong>happy 1.7k!!!!</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 240, 239)\">it’s been a bit since I’ve made a special 😭and AGES since I’ve made a duo bot as a special (since 400 YIKES) I’m horribly inconsistent 💀 I apologize</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 240, 239)\">I’ve mentioned before that mermaids and fae folk will sneak by my no hybrids rule from time to time and this is one of those times 🤍</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 240, 239)\">as always I can’t thank everyone enough for your support! thank you for the well wishes, I’m feeling better &lt;3</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 240, 239)\">I love you all and hope something in your day makes you